      "input": "2 9 12\n8 4 30\n4 6 16\n6 1 13\n6 5 1\n5 2 26\n7 2 10\n3 9 23\n9 3 5\n1 4 7\n4 5 18\n2 5 8\n9 2 19",
      "output": "24 0 42 17 0 1 10 47 19",
